---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---
<section class="relative bg-white pt-20 pb-24 md:pb-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
    
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-edurun-blue/10 via-purple-100/20 to-edurun-purple/10 animate-gradient border border-edurun-blue/20 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 mb-6 md:mb-8 text-xs md:text-sm">
      <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-edurun-blue animate-pulse"></span>
      <span class="font-medium text-edurun-blue tracking-wide">Compatible con Canvas LTI 1.3</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-edurun-dark tracking-tight mb-4 md:mb-6 leading-tight">
      Integridad Académica <br class="hidden md:block" />
      <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-edurun-blue via-purple-500 to-edurun-purple animate-gradient">
        Sin Compromisos.
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-3 md:mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base md:text-xl text-gray-500 mb-8 md:mb-10 px-2">
      Edurun es el entorno de evaluación para Python que mitiga el uso de IA mediante trazabilidad avanzada y contenedores seguros.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-3 md:gap-4 px-4">
      <a href="/contacto" class="glow-on-hover bg-edurun-dark text-white px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all shadow-lg text-center">
        Contáctanos
      </a>
      <a href="/docs/arquitectura" data-astro-reload class="glow-on-hover bg-white text-edurun-dark border-2 border-gray-200 px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all text-center">
        Ver Documentación
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 w-full -translate-x-1/2 h-full z-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-20 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-gradient-to-r from-edurun-blue/30 to-purple-500/30 morph-blob blur-3xl opacity-40"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-20 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-gradient-to-r from-edurun-purple/30 to-pink-500/30 morph-blob blur-3xl opacity-40" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[30rem] h-[30rem] bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400/20 to-purple-400/20 morph-blob blur-3xl opacity-30" style="animation-delay: 4s;"></div>
  </div>
</section>